'''Team NaKuda''' was a [[Swoop racing/Legends|swoop racing]] team. As of [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]], it had become the fourth-highest-ranking swoop team.

The team included the [[Dug/Legends|Dug]] [[Hodrix]] and the [[Cerean/Legends|Cerean]] [[Jo-Mau-Rinti]].

